      <title>城市希望利用人工智能来标记居民的垃圾和回收错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/east-lansing-leduc-look-to-ai-to-better-manage-trash-and-recycling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国密歇根州和加拿大阿尔伯塔省的当地政府正在使用摄像头来举报那些将错误物品放入回收箱或堆肥箱的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/east-lansing-leduc-look-to-ai-to-better-manage-trash-and-recycling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:19:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SolarWinds 首席执行官表示，随着中东销售热潮的兴起，该公司计划在利雅得设立办事处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/solarwinds-plans-riyadh-office-as-mideast-sales-boom-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SolarWinds Corp. 首席执行官苏达卡·拉马克里什纳 (Sudhakar Ramakrishna) 表示，由于其中东业务快速增长，该公司计划明年在沙特阿拉伯首都利雅得开设办事处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/solarwinds-plans-riyadh-office-as-mideast-sales-boom-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:50:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Silver Lake 和 GIC 同意以 17 亿美元收购软件公司 Zuora</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/silver-lake-gic-agree-1-7-billion-deal-for-software-firm-zuora</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银湖管理公司 (Silver Lake Management) 和新加坡 GIC Pte 已同意收购 Zuora Inc.，交易对该软件制造商的估值为 17 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/silver-lake-gic-agree-1-7-billion-deal-for-software-firm-zuora</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印孚瑟斯因 IT 支出复苏乐观而上调销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-on-it-spending-revival-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印孚瑟斯公司今年第二次上调了年度销售预期，表明由于主要经济体的强劲增长和通胀放缓，客户可能会恢复对软件服务的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-on-it-spending-revival-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的帝国可能被欧盟罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/musk-s-empire-risks-being-targeted-by-eu-for-potential-x-fines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟已警告 Google X，其可能会将埃隆·马斯克的其他业务（包括太空探索技术公司和 Neuralink 公司）的收入计入该社交媒体平台的罚款，这种方法将大大增加违反内容审核规则的潜在处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/musk-s-empire-risks-being-targeted-by-eu-for-potential-x-fines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 09:45:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FTX 的 Nishad Singh 敦促纽约法官免除其监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ftx-s-nishad-singh-urges-judge-to-spare-him-from-prison</link>
      <description><![CDATA[已倒闭的加密货币交易所 FTX 的前工程主管请求法官不要因交易所倒闭而将他判入狱，理由是他在起诉联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 的过程中与政府进行了合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ftx-s-nishad-singh-urges-judge-to-spare-him-from-prison</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 04:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Robinhood 为交易者提供期货、指数期权交易机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/robinhood-plans-to-give-traders-access-to-futures-index-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗宾汉市场公司 (Robinhood Markets Inc.) 正在扩大其期货交易和指数期权产品范围，因为这家零售经纪公司旨在吸引更多成熟投资者使用其平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/robinhood-plans-to-give-traders-access-to-futures-index-options</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
